    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is an analog masterpiece in museum-grade condition. Featuring the coveted 3.8L DFI flat-six, the powerplant delivers linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains factory-tight, with PASM active damping and a limited-slip differential ensuring surgical turn-in and high-speed stability. Zero mechanical lash, impeccable compression across all cylinders, and a flawless undercarriage with no signs of heat cycling or oxidation. This is a collector-tier example for the discerning purist seeking peak mechanical harmony.",
